➜幼儿英语绘本故事What Mommies Do Best
http://www.sohu.com/a/420863627_100171577	41901
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/ce71dbd6d78c4cb9bb103a2cb8e84197.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Mommies can teach you how to ride a bicycle, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妈妈能教你骑自行车，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/4763fd2b637045c693d6a0018b2652b4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">make a snowman with you, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和你一起堆雪人，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200925/8956ce8e55084a07b98964bc996c4d04.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
