</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">and bake a delicious cake for your birthday.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能在你生日那天，为你烤一个蛋糕。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/cd06e793a90044a2b3a0d0c116cdb271.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Mommies can help you make a garden grow, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妈妈能帮你打理花园，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/a92510dcc19940a894f2562aea3f541b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">give you a piggyback ride, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把你驮在背上，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/7ef823412e4a46108ded403ca59eabe2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">and take care of you when you're sick. </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能在你生病时，细心照顾你。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200925/ec4837791daa42a2a1f4ae9e2deed92c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Mommies can watch the sun set with you, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妈妈能跟你一起看日落，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200925/5558cafbf2fb46799cf06761b0968daf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">sew the loose button on your teddy bear, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">帮你的泰迪熊缝缝松了的扣子，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200925/963c27010f654edfb0e2dbd05875ae7c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">and hold you when you're feeling sad. </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能在你伤心时，给你温暖的拥抱。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/56f72c316a6142b08c805fd2069d9220.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Mommies can take you trick-or-treating, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妈妈能带你玩“不给糖就捣蛋”的游戏，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200925/64162f6b2a4c44f9b17f06f89bbc6809.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">help you give the dog a bath, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">帮你给狗狗洗澡，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200925/dc324044e79e41b6bdcd6cb9178972e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">and play with you in the park. </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能跟你一起去公园玩耍。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200925/0906fd85ba74477e97c595c8d41d83e2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">Mommies can read you a bedtime story, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">妈妈能给你讲睡前故事，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200925/8f5dd3b1874c4e0d8806c205ac6ed7af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">tuck you in, </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">帮你盖好被子,</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/e840f8dd03a640028bc649cacf5b09ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">and kiss you good-night. </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还能亲亲你，跟你说晚安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">And best of all, mommies can give you lots and lots of love!</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最棒的是，妈妈能给你很多很多的爱！</p>